  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chat Ragdoll Racing</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is fully physics-based ragdoll animated simulation game where Twitch Streamers can host games for their communities and have people race against each other in a wild physics-based world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511350/extras/1436b7d863b0b2a2b10d7b29eeef2202.poster.avif?t=1746655465\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511350/extras/1436b7d863b0b2a2b10d7b29eeef2202.webm?t=1746655465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511350/extras/1436b7d863b0b2a2b10d7b29eeef2202.mp4?t=1746655465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural Ragdoll Physics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twitch Chat integration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local leaderboard for streamer communities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destructable environment</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511350/extras/0b4c0c355aae17fc9d62d8672f0114e4.poster.avif?t=1746655465\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511350/extras/0b4c0c355aae17fc9d62d8672f0114e4.webm?t=1746655465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511350/extras/0b4c0c355aae17fc9d62d8672f0114e4.mp4?t=1746655465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streamer has a lot of control how the characters and the map behaves.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control individual muscles in character animation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place physical traps into the world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab individual players and throw them around</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
